// If rover and goal and is damaged, then send complete notification OR send damage help notification?
// If reboot fails, go to ask help, or try rebooting again? -> Assume side rover alaays works for now. -> If wrong rover also send, then force the other rover id to be sent? Then how deep will this recurse?
